Comment: 0,0:01:19.30,0:01:25.52,SongOP,ja,0,0,0,,BUGEI! 二刀流　ムサシ
Comment: 0,0:01:25.52,0:01:28.51,SongOP,ja,0,0,0,,明日は　輝くぞ
Comment: 0,0:01:28.51,0:01:30.98,SongOP,ja,0,0,0,,鍔迫り合いの音が
Comment: 0,0:01:30.98,0:01:33.48,SongOP,ja,0,0,0,,眩しい人生
